                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10215" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1510</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">339 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广之旅：开着房车去旅行</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">GZL: Traveling in an RV</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">姜彩芬，郑晓薇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广州大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广州广之旅国际旅行社股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">顾客体验；顾客满意；消费者教育；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">customer experience; customer satisfaction; consumer education</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了华南大型旅行社广州广之旅国际旅行社股份有限公司（以下简称“广之旅”）在探索中发展房车旅游业务到努力成为行业标杆的过程。当露营、野餐和房车旅行之风在年轻人中吹起时，广之旅迅速响应市场，开始组建专业房车业务团队，购置房车产品。在市场推广初期，由于用户认知和市场教育不足，从顾客体验热潮到口碑逆跌不过几个月。为了升级顾客体验，广之旅开始进行系统性破局，不仅优化房车空间，还针对各种场景进行个性化定制、激活各类人群的需求，也因此实现了公司业务的规模性增长。站在新的起点，广之旅致力于引领一种全新的生活方式。通过极致细腻的服务打造标杆级顾客体验，希望每一位顾客在房车旅行中都能满意。广之旅也将承担市场教育者的角色，化解消费者的疑虑，期待与消费者共同实现从“向往”到“体验”再到“热爱”的转变，让房车旅行作为一种生活方式真正融入人们的日常生活。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case tells the story of GZL&#39;s RV travel business as it develops through exploration and strives to become an industry benchmark. When the wind of camping, picnicking, and RV travel was blowing among young people, GZL quickly responded to the market and began to form a professional RV business team. It began to set up a professional caravan business team and acquired caravan products. In the early stage of market promotion, due to the lack of user awareness and market education, it took only a few months from the user experience boom to the reverse decline of word of mouth. In order to upgrade the user experience, GZL began to make systematic breakthroughs, not only to optimize the caravan space, but also to personalize for a variety of scenarios, activating the needs of all kinds of people, and then realize the growth of the company&#39;s business scale. Standing at a new starting point, GZL is committed to pioneering an entirely new lifestyle. By delivering exceptionally refined service to create benchmark customer experiences, we strive for every traveler to find satisfaction in their RV journeys. GZL will also assume the role of market educator, addressing consumer concerns and working alongside travelers to transform their aspirations into experiences and ultimately into a passion. We aim to integrate RV travel as a lifestyle into people&#39;s daily lives.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》、《消费者行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">顾客体验；顾客满意；消费者教育</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
